
I. about interface 
1. interface of infrastrucure (repository, httpclient, s3) place in domain/repository, domain/service
because these interface using by usecase (usecase depend on domain)
2. interface of usecase place in same folder usecase
because these interface using by presentation (presentation depend on usecase)

II. about dto
1. dto of infrastructure only use in infrastructure layer
2. dto in usecase can use in usecase and presentation layer
3. entities, Value Object, Domain Rule Constants use in domain and usecase
